<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Bot Team</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .feature-list {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Bot Team!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{ user_name }}</strong>,</p>

        <p>We're excited to have you on board! This is an HTML version of the welcome email with nice formatting.</p>

        <div class="feature-list">
            <h3>Here's what you can expect:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Friendly automated emails from our bot team</li>
                <li>Quick responses to your requests</li>
                <li>Reliable service 24/7</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The Bot Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an example email template for Mabel.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
